Class RealmAuditServiceProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.audit.AuditServiceProxy
      • org.forgerock.openam.audit.RealmAuditServiceProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.forgerock.audit.AuditService, org.forgerock.json.resource.RequestHandler, AMAuditService

    public class RealmAuditServiceProxy
extends org.forgerock.audit.AuditServiceProxy
implements AMAuditService
    Extension of the commons AuditServiceProxy that allows for OpenAM specific configuration to be exposed in a thread-safe way.
    Since:
    13.0.0

        Description copied from interface: AMAuditService
